_sText:
Hi guys, this is just a remake or remix of the original ba_jail_electric.
But it is based on ba_jail_electric_razor_v2_v2
Some new Futures to play are added, like a roulette room(you can see it on the picture)
Also some new escape ways are added.
And of course weapons!
Good looking things like custom textures or lights are still not in the map for gameplay reasons!!!
So dont tell me the textures are bad :)

So I hope you enjoy it :)

If there are any bugs, please report them as fast as you can!
